{
  "steps": [
    
    {
        "banner": {
            "text": "Let's learn how the Animation part works and how to paint your own cool light sprites",
            "next_button": true
        },
        "beacon": {
            "target": "banner-button",
            "offset": 0
        }
    },
    {
        "banner": {
            "text":"We're going to animate a bouncy ball, this is one of the first things animators learn",
            "next_button": true
        },
        "beacon": {
            "target": "banner-button",
            "offset": 0
        },
        "tooltips":[
          {
            "location":"banner-button",
            "position":"bottom",
            "offset": 150,
            "text":"<img src='/assets/stories/assets/pixel_intro_4/ball.gif' width='150' />"
          }
        ]
    },
    {
      "banner":{
        "text":"We need to add an Animation part, click here"
      },
      "beacon":{
        "target":"add-part-button"
      },
      "validation":{
        "open-parts":true
      }
    },
    {
      "beacon":{
        "target":"parts-panel-light-animation"
      },
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "location":"parts-panel",
          "position":"top",
          "text":"Add a light Animation"
        }
      ],
      "validation":{
        "add-part":{
          "type":"light-animation",
          "id":"part_0"
        }
      }
    },    
    {
      "beacon":{
        "target":{
          "path":"parts-controls",
          "part":"part_0"
        },
        "angle":180,
        "offset":30
      },
      "banner":{
        "text":"Click on the Animation part to open the ✨Animation Editor✨"
      },
      "validation":{
        "open-part-settings":{
          "target":"part_0"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "text":"Let's start by picking a nice color",
          "location":"animation-editor-colors",
          "position":"top"
        }
      ],
      "beacon": {
          "target": "animation-editor-colors",
          "offset": 0
      },
      "validation":{
        "light-animation-color-changed":true
      }
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "text":"Start drawing your ball on the left like this<br><img src='/assets/stories/assets/pixel_intro_4/ball1.png' width='100' />",
          "location":"animation-editor-canvas",
          "position":"top"
        }
      ],
      "beacon": {
          "target": "animation-editor-canvas",
          "offset": 0
      },
      "validation":{
        "light-animation-paint":{
          "tool":"draw"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "text":"Cool, click Next when you are done<br><img src='/assets/stories/assets/pixel_intro_4/ball1.png' width='100' />",
          "location":"animation-editor-canvas",
          "position":"top",
          "next_button":true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "text":"This is where your frames are stored. Frames are like pages in a flipbook, by cycling through them your pictures come to life",
          "location":"animation-editor-frames",
          "position":"top",
          "next_button":true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "location":"animation-editor-add-frame-button",
          "position":"top",
          "text":"Let's add a new frame to<br> your Animation with this button"
        }
      ],
      "beacon": {
          "target": "animation-editor-add-frame-button",
          "offset": 0
      },
      "validation":{
        "light-animation-add-frame":true
      }
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "text":"Draw the ball again a bit lower to the ground and to the right, click Next when you are done<br><img src='/assets/stories/assets/pixel_intro_4/ball2.png' width='100' />",
          "location":"animation-editor-canvas",
          "position":"top",
          "next_button":true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "location":"animation-editor-add-frame-button",
          "position":"top",
          "text":"Add another frame"
        }
      ],
      "beacon": {
          "target": "animation-editor-add-frame-button",
          "offset": 0
      },
      "validation":{
        "light-animation-add-frame":true
      }
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "text":"Pssst I'll tell you one of the secrets to great animation, it's called <strong>Squash and Stretch</strong><br><img src='/assets/stories/assets/pixel_intro_4/judoka.png' width='100' />",
          "location":"animation-editor-canvas",
          "position":"top",
          "next_button":true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "text":"When something is moving fast it should be drawn <strong>Stretched</strong> out<br><img src='/assets/stories/assets/pixel_intro_4/stretch.png' width='100' />",
          "location":"animation-editor-canvas",
          "position":"top",
          "next_button":true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "text":"If it bumps into a wall of floor it should <strong>Squash</strong><br><img src='/assets/stories/assets/pixel_intro_4/squash.png' width='100' />",
          "location":"animation-editor-canvas",
          "position":"top",
          "next_button":true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "text":"Let's draw the ball <strong>squashed</strong> against the floor for this frame<br><img src='/assets/stories/assets/pixel_intro_4/ball3.png' width='100' />",
          "location":"animation-editor-canvas",
          "position":"top",
          "next_button":true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "location":"animation-editor-add-frame-button",
          "position":"top",
          "text":"Add another frame"
        }
      ],
      "beacon": {
          "target": "animation-editor-add-frame-button",
          "offset": 0
      },
      "validation":{
        "light-animation-add-frame":true
      }
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "text":"The ball is bouncing hard off the floor so draw it <strong>stretched</strong> out and flying off to the right<br><img src='/assets/stories/assets/pixel_intro_4/ball4.png' width='100' />",
          "location":"animation-editor-canvas",
          "position":"top",
          "next_button":true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "location":"animation-editor-add-frame-button",
          "position":"top",
          "text":"Let's add one more frame"
        }
      ],
      "beacon": {
          "target": "animation-editor-add-frame-button",
          "offset": 0
      },
      "validation":{
        "light-animation-add-frame":true
      }
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "text":"One last frame, draw the ball leaving the stage like this<br><img src='/assets/stories/assets/pixel_intro_4/ball5.png' width='100' />",
          "location":"animation-editor-canvas",
          "position":"top",
          "next_button":true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "location":"animation-editor-preview-button",
          "position":"top",
          "text":"Your animation is finished now for the best bit, hit the play button to watch it!"
        }
      ],
      "beacon":{
        "target":"animation-editor-preview-button"
      },
      "validation":{
        "light-animation-preview-changed":{
          "value":"running"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "location":"animation-editor-preview-button",
          "position":"top",
          "text":"Click again when you want to stop"
        }
      ],
      "beacon":{
        "target":"animation-editor-preview-button"
      },
      "validation":{
        "light-animation-preview-changed":{
          "value":"stopped"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "tooltips":[
        {
          "location":"animation-editor",
          "position":"top",
          "text":"We're ready to get back to coding, click the <strong>Done</strong> button"
        }
      ],
      "validation":{
        "close-part-settings":true
      }
    },
    {
        "banner": {
            "text": "Let's add a bit of code to play it, open the Animation tray"
        },
        "beacon": {
            "target": {
                "category": {
                    "part": "part_0"
                }
            }
        },
        "validation": {
            "blockly": {
                "open-flyout": {
                    "part": "part_0"
                }
            }
        }
    },
    {
        "banner": {
            "text": "This block plays and loops the animation, drag it onto your code space"
        },
        "beacon": {
            "target": {
                "flyout_block": {
                    "part": "part_0",
                    "type": "animation_play"
                }
            }
        },
        "validation": {
            "blockly": {
                "create": {
                    "target": "part_0",
                    "type": "animation_play",
                    "id": "block_0"
                }
            }
        }
    },
    {
        "banner": {
            "text": "Connect it to this block"
        },
        "beacon": {
            "target": {
                "block": {
                    "id": null,
                    "rawId": "default_part_event_id"
                }
            }
        },
        "validation": {
            "blockly": {
                "connect": {
                    "parent": {
                        "id": null,
                        "rawId": "default_part_event_id",
                        "inputName": "DO"
                    },
                    "target": "block_0"
                }
            }
        },
        "phantom_block": {
            "location": {
                "block": {
                    "id": null,
                    "rawId": "default_part_event_id"
                }
            },
            "target": "DO"
        }
    },
    {
        "banner": {
            "text": "Perfectly painted pixels! Well done",
            "next_button": true
        },
        "beacon": {
            "target": "banner-button",
            "offset": 0
        }
    },
    {
        "banner": {
            "text": "Now you're ready to explore the other challenges",
            "next_button": true
        },
        "beacon": {
            "target": "banner-button",
            "offset": 0
        }
    }
  ],
  "parts": ["light-animation"],
  "mode": "lightboard",
  "modules": []
}
